name: Bergeland high school
directions:
There are single stall/gender neutral bathrooms on the 2nd and 3rd floor. The ground floor has gendered bathrooms with around five or six stalls each. I’ve never been to the 4th floor myself and can’t say wether or not there are bathrooms there or if they’re gender neutral.

These bathrooms are not very accessible if you struggle with going up and down stairs, and the hallways/stairwells are rather narrow.
comment: This is a school and is therefore only open during school hours.
